  "body": "Use of React, Suspense and Lazy is increasing bundle size.\r\n\r\nI created a bundle with use of Suspense lazy, its size was **127mb**.\r\nThen I removed the use of Suspense lazy, and did normal imports, in result, the build was **80mb** only.\r\n\r\nBuild size should not get affected.\r\n\r\nI am using React app created via create-react-app.\r\n",
